Noel Roeim Fisher -LRB- born March 13 , 1984 -RRB- is a Canadian actor .
He is known for his portrayal of Mickey Milkovich on the Showtime series Shameless , as well as his portrayal of Cael Malloy on the FX series The Riches .
He played Ellison `` Cotton Top '' Mounts in the Emmy Award -- winning miniseries Hatfields & McCoys as well as Vladimir , a 1500-year-old vampire in The Twilight Saga : Breaking Dawn -- Part 2 , and Michelangelo in Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles and its sequel Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles : Out of the Shadows .
He also has had a substantial number of roles in shows such as Criminal Minds : Suspect Behavior , Lie to Me , Bones , and Law & Order : Special Victims Unit .